messageBody:
Apologies for the familiar text, but I don't have any short original pangrams handy. While this question is primarily aimed at Quikscript readers who don't know Shavian, I'm opening it to everyone (although please do say what you do know, and how well you know it).

  • Can you read this, or at least figure out most of what it says?
  • If you had to read something on a computer in Quikscript made with letterforms like this, would you be able to? If not, how long do you think it would take?

I'll explain why I'm asking in a couple days.
